Package: rustyfoot
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         liblilv-0-0,
         libjack-jackd2-0 | libjack0,
         rustyfoot-modhost
Recommends: jack-capture
Description: Web-based pedalboard manager for MOD Audio devices
 Rust reimplementation of the mod-ui web server for managing
 LV2 audio plugin pedalboards. Provides a browser-based interface
 for building, saving, and loading pedalboard configurations with
 real-time audio processing via mod-host and JACK.
